Network Switch Scheduling 

How to Run

1. Compile

g++ switch_scheduler.cpp -o switch_scheduler

2. Run Simulation

./switch_scheduler

 3. Generate Graphs

python part4_visualization.py


What It Does

 Runs 3 algorithms:

  * FIFO
  * VOQ (Optimal)
  * VOQ (iSLIP)

Outputs:

  * Total Service Time
  * Backlog data
  * Graphs comparing performance


